Dia nak pergi jumpa pakar bedah plastik.

46
00:05:01,135 --> 00:05:02,529
Saya hampir tak dapat halang dia.

47
00:05:03,135 --> 00:05:05,199
- Kenapa awak buat begitu? - Kenapa saya...

48
00:05:05,905 --> 00:05:09,099
