208
00:17:17,965 --> 00:17:19,105
Kenapa?

209
00:17:19,105 --> 00:17:21,030
Sebab saya nak novel saya berada dalam 10 teratas.

210
00:17:22,375 --> 00:17:23,500
Itu saja sebabnya?

211
00:17:25,744 --> 00:17:26,839
Ya.

212
00:17:30,175 --> 00:17:32,639
Kalau begitu, e-mel saya atau mesej saya.

213
00:17:33,145 --> 00:17:35,149
Kalau awak langgar kontrak kita...

214
00:17:37,514 --> 00:17:40,649
...saya akan beritahu Hyun Kyu yang awak cium saya.

215
00:17:41,254 --> 00:17:43,254
- Bolehkah awak buat begitu? - Awak fikir saya tak mampu?

216
00:17:43,254 --> 00:17:45,560
Saya rasa tak boleh.

217
00:17:47,225 --> 00:17:49,490
Kalau boleh, beritahulah dia.

218
00:17:53,234 --> 00:17:54,329
Biar betul.

219
00:17:55,274 --> 00:17:56,470
Dia begitu menjengkelkan.

220
00:18:11,054 --> 00:18:13,419
Pastikan awak tak terdedah pada elemen ini.

221
00:18:27,665 --> 00:18:28,770
Ada apa?

222
00:18:30,504 --> 00:18:31,669
Apa?

223
00:18:32,304 --> 00:18:35,409
